firm mr asali received an mba from columbia business school and a bs in accounting from virginia tech ms roger is a managing director and general counsel of harbinger capital partners and had joined the spectrum board in june  in addition the board elected david maura to the position of chairman of the board and mr asali as vice chairman of the board mr maura and mr asali will serve in their respective positions in accordance with the company’s amended and restated bylaws and at the discretion of the board mr maura joined the spectrum board in june  and was previously serving as the interim chairman of the board i have worked with omar for the last several years at harbinger capital partners and have really come to respect his sound judgment and advice” said david maura chairman of the board “i look forward to partnering with omar to continue to drive the strategic vision of spectrum brands i also want to thank the entire board for their confidence in me i could not be more proud of our management team led by david lumley and i am excited and optimistic about the future as we continue to build a firstclass global consumer products company our spectrum value model is a leader in the market place and we are committed to building shareholder value in the months and years to come about spectrum brands holdings inc spectrum brands holdings inc a member of the russell  index is a diversified global consumer products company and a leading supplier of batteries shaving and grooming products personal care products small household appliances specialty pet supplies lawn  garden and home pest control products personal insect repellents and portable lighting helping to meet the needs of consumers worldwide the company offers a broad portfolio of marketleading and widely trusted brands including rayovac® remington® varta® george foreman® black  decker® toastmaster® tetra® marineland® nature’s miracle® dingo® in® littermaid® spectracide® cutter® repel® and hot shot® spectrum brands holdings products are sold by the worlds top  retailers and are available in more than one million stores in more than  countries around the world spectrum brands holdings generated net sales of  billion from continuing operations in fiscal  for more information visit wwwspectrumbrandscom contacts spectrum brands holdings incdave prichard  contacts spectrum brands holdings incdave prichard  search advanced news search advanced news search log in sign up omar m asali  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in omar m asali former president chief executive officer and director at hrg group inc view full profile are you omar m asali claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view omar m asalis full profile with equilar atlas you can identify corporate executives in omar m asalis network and community follow changes in omar m asalis employment and moneyinmotion connect with omar m asali through your network of contacts omar m asalis executive work history past to view omar m asalis complete executive work history sign up now education bs virginia tech mba columbia university age      sign up for equilar atlas and view omar m asalis full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like omar m asali more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in omar m asalis network and community follow changes in omar m asalis employment and moneyinmotion connect with omar m asali through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example omar m asali omar m asalis connections  sign up now to view omar m asalis  connections » david r lumley board member the valspar corporation gerald luterman lead independent director hrg group inc frank ianna board member hrg group inc douglas l martin executive vice president and chief financial officer spectrum brands holdings inc anthony l genito fo